      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should check with them but my doctor is super hard to reach and i have to wait weeks for an appointment. it's kinda frustrating because i feel so much better than i did when i started. if i've been consistent with my diet and i feel fine, isn't it possible my body just needs less of it now? like, couldn't i just try the 2mg for a week and see how i feel? it seems safer than being on too much medication.",
